info.name: cyber mazter
info.description: Here's something special about your theme: it doesn’t just look sharp and techy, but it also transforms the mundane browsing experience into a scene straight out of a cyberpunk thriller. The green-on-black color scheme evokes the legendary command-line interfaces that hackers are famous for. Each time you open a new tab or type a search query, it feels like you’re diving into the digital depths, unearthing secrets and cutting through the noise. It’s not just a theme—it’s an experience.
